AgiBot Genie — Tier 1 (actively supported) robot family.

This is the canonical platform for the GenieSim stack.  Every release of
genie_sim_engine, genie_sim_bringup, and the physics_params.yaml gain
tables is validated against G2 variants here.

Variants under g2/ pair the body with arm and gripper options:

  - body:    g2  (one body)
  - arm:     crs | crsB
  - gripper: omnipicker | swiftpicker

Selected at launch time via the scene yaml robot.robot_source block:

  robot_source:
    robot_model: genie
    body:    g2
    arm:     crsB
    gripper: swiftpicker

Canonical scenes for this robot live in
share/genie_sim_bringup/config/scene_flat_g2_*.yaml; canonical launchers
live in share/genie_sim_bringup/config/launcher_newton_*.yaml.

Other robots in this package (agilex/aloha, agilex/piper, arx/x5,
arx/acone, franka/fr3, universal_robots/ur5) are Tier 2 — kept buildable
but not continuously validated.  See ../../AGENTS.md for the full
support-tier policy.
